### C/C++ 智能助教平台 API 测试
### 使用 REST Client 扩展或 Postman 测试

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = mock_token_123

### ============================================
### 认证相关
### ============================================

### 1. 用户登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. 用户注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "name": "新用户"
}

### 3. 获取当前用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 用户相关
### ============================================

### 4. 获取用户统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/stats

### ============================================
### 题目相关
### ============================================

### 5. 获取题目列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/problems?page=1&pageSize=10

### 6. 筛选题目（Easy 难度）
GET {{baseUrl}}/problems?difficulty=Easy&category=数组

### 7. 搜索题目
GET {{baseUrl}}/problems?search=链表

### 8. 获取题目详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/problems/1

### ============================================
### 代码相关
### ============================================

### 9. 运行代码
POST {{baseUrl}}/code/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "#include <iostream>\nusing namespace std;\nint main() {\n  cout << \"Hello World!\" << endl;\n  return 0;\n}",
  "language": "cpp",
  "input": ""
}

### 10. 提交代码
POST {{baseUrl}}/code/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "problemId": "1",
  "code": "#include <vector>\nusing namespace std;\nvector<int> twoSum(vector<int>& nums, int target) {\n  // solution here\n}",
  "language": "cpp"
}

### ============================================
### 面试相关
### ============================================

### 11. 获取面试模板
GET {{baseUrl}}/interviews/templates

### 12. 创建面试会话
POST {{baseUrl}}/interviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "C++ 基础面试",
  "type": "technical",
  "templateId": "cpp-basics"
}

### 13. 获取面试列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/interviews

### 14. 获取面试详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/interviews/1

### 15. 发送面试消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/interviews/1/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "我准备好了，可以开始面试。"
}

### 16. 删除面试会话
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/interviews/1

### ============================================
### 学习路径
### ============================================

### 17. 获取学习路径列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/learning-paths

### 18. 获取学习路径详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/learning-paths/1

### 19. 更新学习进度
POST {{baseUrl}}/learning-paths/1/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stepId": 5,
  "completed": true
}

### ============================================
### 知识库
### ============================================

### 20. 获取知识库分类
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/categories

### 21. 获取知识文章列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge?page=1&pageSize=10

### 22. 筛选文章（按分类）
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge?category=pointer&difficulty=Medium

### 23. 搜索文章
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge?search=智能指针

### 24. 获取文章详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/1

### ============================================
### 能力雷达图
### ============================================

### 25. 获取能力雷达图
GET {{baseUrl}}/capability-radar?userId=1

### 26. 更新能力雷达图
POST {{baseUrl}}/capability-radar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1",
  "basicSyntax": 90,
  "memoryManagement": 75,
  "dataStructures": 85,
  "oop": 80,
  "stlLibrary": 88,
  "systemProgramming": 70
}

